title: DESIGNER VIDEO: OTTO sensor pump
description:
Umbra Designer Dennis Cheng explains his new product for Umbra's 2012 collection

OTTO sensor pump 
• Available in two colours.
• Ideal in both the kitchen and bathroom.
• Helps reduce germ transfer with its no touch technology..
